如果我們同時用一堆問題攻擊她，

339
00:21:58,230 --> 00:22:00,355
she'd feel overwhelmed.
她會無法承受的。

340
00:22:01,103 --> 00:22:03,825
It could be too much of a shock for her.
可能會把她嚇死吧。

341
00:22:03,925 --> 00:22:06,308
So, Karolina will talk to her first
所以呢，Karolina會先去跟她談話，

342
00:22:06,600 --> 00:22:09,729
and then I'll go and ask her my questions.
然後之後再換我去問我的問題，

343
00:22:09,829 --> 00:22:12,276
I think everything should be fine.
我想這樣就沒問題了。

344
00:22:16,450 --> 00:22:17,492
Hello.
你好。

345
00:22:17,692 --> 00:22:18,957
Hi Mum.
嗨，媽。

346
00:22:19,613 --> 00:22:21,408
Hi Karolinka.
嗨，Karolinka。

347
00:22:21,821 --> 00:22:23,401
I was calling you yesterday. 
我昨天打電話給你。

348
00:22:23,501 --> 00:22:24,437
You didn't answer.
你沒有接。

349
00:22:24,612 --> 00:22:27,017
I left my mobile at work.
我把手機放在公司了

350
00:22:27,418 --> 00:22:29,475
Have you read my message?
你看到我的簡訊了嗎？

351
00:22:29,806 --> 00:22:31,646
I haven't checked the messages.
我還沒看

352
00:22:31,746 --> 00:22:33,940
They brought my phone in the morning.
他們今天早上才幫我把手機帶來。

353
00:22:34,531 --> 00:22:35,813
I'm going to take a bath now
我現在去洗個澡，

354
00:22:35,913 --> 00:22:37,047
and we'll meet later on.
等等我們來見面。

355
00:22:37,418 --> 00:22:40,765
Listen, I've got something to do now.
嘿聽著，我現在有點忙，

356
00:22:40,865 --> 00:22:44,919
Let's meet at 5 o'clock by the Eiffel Tower.
我們五點在艾菲爾鐵塔碰面吧！

357
00:22:45,332 --> 00:22:45,996
O.K.
沒問題。

358
00:22:46,380 --> 00:22:50,841
Fine. My heart's beating so hard. What?
很好。 我心跳超快的。什麼？

359
00:22:51,299 --> 00:22:53,880
So, 5 o'clock by the Eiffel Tower.
所以，五點在艾菲爾鐵塔？

360
00:22:54,088 --> 00:22:55,415
Right.
對

361
00:22:55,524 --> 00:22:57,223
How do you like it here?
你喜歡這裡嗎？

362
00:22:57,445 --> 00:23:01,326
It's nice. A totally different world.
很棒阿，是一個完全不同的世界

363
00:23:01,877 --> 00:23:04,398
It seems nice to tourists, but it's different
對觀光客來說很棒，

364
00:23:04,498 --> 00:23:06,496
for people who work here.
但是對在這裡工作的人來說卻完全不同。

365
00:23:06,699 --> 00:23:09,405
I guess so.
我猜也是

366
00:23:10,650 --> 00:23:15,741
I can see that she misses us and really cares.
我感覺的到她很想念而且很在乎我們，

367
00:23:15,841 --> 00:23:19,299
She's interested in how we live.
她想知道我們過的如何。

368
00:23:21,177 --> 00:23:24,710
It looks good. Maybe not everything is perfect,
感覺還不錯。也許不會每件事情都超完美，

369
00:23:24,810 --> 00:23:26,497
but it's a good start.
但這是一個好的開始。

370
00:23:28,322 --> 00:23:30,256
It's difficult to meet somebody who
要去見一個多年前拋棄

371
00:23:30,356 --> 00:23:32,070
abandoned you many years ago.
你的人真的是滿困難的。

372
00:23:32,176 --> 00:23:34,902
You hate this person,
你恨這個人，

373
00:23:35,002 --> 00:23:40,401
but you're also somehow attracted to her.
但你也不知為何被她吸引。

374
00:23:40,866 --> 00:23:45,703
You just feel it's the right moment to meet up,
你只是覺得它是一個適合見面的時機，

375
00:23:45,803 --> 00:23:49,341
but it's very difficult emotionally.
但是感情上還是滿難的。

376
00:23:49,751 --> 00:23:53,394
My hands are trembling. I feel like fainting.
我的手一直發抖。我覺得好像快昏倒了，

377
00:23:53,494 --> 00:23:57,079
Thousands of thoughts are racing through my head.
千萬個思緒在我腦海裡狂奔。

378
00:23:57,475 --> 00:23:59,885
I can control myself now but when we meet
我現在可以控制自己，

379
00:23:59,985 --> 00:24:02,250
I won't be able to utter a word.
但當我們見面時我無法說出一個字。

380
00:24:02,586 --> 00:24:06,438
I'll just stand still and stare at her.
我只會站在那邊然後盯著她。

381
00:24:06,538 --> 00:24:08,731
Sorry, I need a drink.
不好意思，我需要喝一杯。

382
00:24:16,884 --> 00:24:19,812
Right next to the entrance. Can you hear me?
在入口的右邊，你聽的到嘛？

383
00:24:20,157 --> 00:24:22,157
The entrance to where?
入口在哪裡？

384
00:24:22,850 --> 00:24:25,941
There's a white kiosk here.
這裡有白色的展示牌。

385
00:24:26,041 --> 00:24:29,216
On your way from… What?
從你的方向......什麼？

386
00:24:29,605 --> 00:24:30,766
By the stairs?
在樓梯旁邊嗎？

387
00:24:31,136 --> 00:24:33,654
Fuck, I don't see any stairs here.
幹！我沒看到這裡有任何樓梯。

388
00:24:33,926 --> 00:24:35,926
You don't?
你沒看到？

389
00:24:36,039 --> 00:24:37,572
I don't. Wait. 
我沒有。等一下。

390
00:24:37,672 --> 00:24:41,684
There's a sign over there. Jesus… What?
這裡有一個標誌。耶穌......什麼？

391
00:24:45,020 --> 00:24:49,178
Are you by the Eiffel Tower now?
你現在是在艾菲爾鐵塔旁邊嗎？

392
00:24:49,648 --> 00:24:53,189
Yes. Let's meet right in the middle
對，我們在鐵塔正

393
00:24:53,289 --> 00:24:56,662
beneath the Eiffel Tower, O.K.?
下方集合這樣好不好？

394
00:24:56,887 --> 00:24:58,473
O.K. How are you dressed?
沒問題。你穿什麼呢？

395
00:24:58,711 --> 00:25:03,366
Dark brown trousers and a red-brown-white top
深棕色長褲和紅色棕色白色上衣。

396
00:25:25,297 --> 00:25:27,904
I'm glad I've recorded this video-letter for her.
我很高興我錄了這個影片當信先給她。

397
00:25:28,004 --> 00:25:29,973
She'll have an opportunity to see me.
她就會有機會看看我的樣子。

398
00:25:30,313 --> 00:25:36,409
She'll meet Karolina, but she'll also see me.
她會見到Karolina，但也會先用影像見到我。

399
00:25:37,067 --> 00:25:40,986
I wonder what her reaction will be
當她看到我在螢幕上的時候

400
00:25:41,086 --> 00:25:43,883
when she sees me on tape.
會是什麼反應呢？

401
00:26:32,149 --> 00:26:34,699
Good morning. This is Bożena.
早安，這是 Bożena的手機。

402
00:26:34,799 --> 00:26:36,727
Please, leave your message.
請留下您的訊息。

403
00:28:10,107 --> 00:28:13,024
I've always wanted to have a mother.
我一直想要有一位母親。

404
00:28:13,284 --> 00:28:17,166
I haven't had my mother for so many years
因為你的遠離，我有那麼多年都沒有母親。

405
00:28:17,266 --> 00:28:21,344
because you've been away. I hope it'll change now.
我希望這一切現在將會改變。

406
00:28:21,684 --> 00:28:23,960
I don't want you to show up for 5 minutes
我不想要你出現五分鐘，

407
00:28:24,060 --> 00:28:26,246
and then disappear for another 14 years.
然後又消失個14年。

408
00:28:26,602 --> 00:28:31,217
I want you to stay with me for good.
我希望你永遠留在我身邊。

409
00:28:38,873 --> 00:28:43,853
Many people have told me that I look just like you.
很多人告訴我，我們長得一模一樣。

410
00:28:43,983 --> 00:28:47,700
The same height, same hair, same eyes.
相同的高度，同樣的頭髮，一樣的眼睛。

411
00:28:47,800 --> 00:28:50,129
We'll see if it's true.
到時候我們就知道了。

